---
import BaseLayout from "../BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="How I Work | Shay Mental Health"
  description="Learn about Jami Sweeney's approach to therapy for children, adolescents, and adults in Washington."
>

  <h1>How I Work</h1>

  <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; max-width: 65ch; color: #444; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    As a therapist trained in working with children and adolescents, I bring a deep understanding 
    of the unique challenges young people face&#8212;and I also enjoy supporting adults navigating 
    life&#8217;s transitions.
  </p>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>A Space Where You Feel Seen</h2>
    <p>
      I strive to create a safe, welcoming space where you can feel seen, heard, and empowered. 
      Whether you&#8217;re a child, a teenager, or an adult, my goal is to meet you exactly where 
      you are&#8212;without judgment, and with genuine curiosity about what matters most to you.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>My Approach</h2>
    <p>
      My work is grounded in evidence-based practices, including Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), 
      Dialectical Behavior Therapy (DBT), and other proven strategies&#8212;tailored to fit your 
      individual needs. I don&#8217;t believe in a one-size-fits-all approach. Instead, I draw from 
      a range of tools and adapt them to your age, temperament, and goals.
    </p>
    <p>
      I believe therapy is not just about addressing mental health concerns&#8212;it&#8217;s about 
      helping you discover your strengths, deepen your resilience, and move toward a more connected, 
      fulfilling life.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Who I Work With</h2>
    <div class="grid cols3" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Children</h3>
        <p>Warm, structured support for younger children navigating anxiety, behavior, school challenges, and family changes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Adolescents</h3>
        <p>A judgment-free space for teens working through identity, relationships, mood, and the pressures of growing up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Adults</h3>
        <p>Support for adults navigating life transitions, stress, relationships, and personal growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
    <a class="btn primary" href="/shaymentalhealth-site/contact">Request a consultation</a>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
